{"tid":1308214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒：美國考慮暫停制裁北韓18個月","createTime":"2019-07-12T00:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T03:23:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3dddbb4d9b938548fc3ce2308a348241aff3873","tid":1308214,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:01:17.000Z","msg":"韓媒：美國考慮暫停制裁北韓18個月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2850065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2850065&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0HGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=d0d86ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2850065&h=4d3b9c62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2850065</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕外媒引述南韓媒體報導稱，美國正在考慮暫停對北韓的一些制裁12至18個月，以換取北韓凍結核武計畫。<br />\n《彭博》報導，南韓媒體《韓聯社》援引一名身分不明的白宮親近人士的消息指出，川普政府考慮支持解除聯合國對北韓煤炭和紡織品出口的限制，以打破無核化談判的僵局。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》指出，作為交換條件，北韓領導人金正恩將被要求拆除寧邊核設施，並全面停止核武計畫。如果北韓未達成協議，將重新實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，暫停制裁將為金正恩政權恢復寶貴的收入來源。美國與北韓預計最快將在5個月內舉行首次工作會談。<br />\n<br />\n自北韓2016年9月進行第5次核試活動以來，聯合國安理會已5度通過制裁北韓的決議，從限制北韓進口石油到禁止出口煤鐵。<br />\n《韓聯社》援引白宮親近人士的話指出，暫停制裁有助於長期對立的兩國建立信任關係，並在北韓採取進一步裁軍步驟時，提供一個可以擴大的模式。"},{"pid":"f58610bb20d27017747eba161543262f594f0bfd","tid":1308214,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T00:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac49419b5783a93f797f538bbec904c91151606","tid":1308214,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"對準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb4603094798cf0e4cd6dbfec11ae58a356336e","tid":1308214,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"愛美金定愛人仔<br />\n金金：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730b1594739570b237ff26273a572ced130254c7","tid":1308214,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"南韓屌鳩緊日本，因日本話南韓穿櫃台底"},{"pid":"388c35063ed8b76ec98893753085f773c5d66309","tid":1308214,"uid":265179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"作為交換條件, 一定要搞習犬犬後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}